ook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Encyclopedia+of+the+middle+passage&amp;rft.pages=xxi%2C+xxxiii-xxxiv&amp;rft.pub=Greenwood+Press&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-313-33480-1&amp;rft.aulast=Falola&amp;rft.aufirst=Toyin&amp;rft.au=Warnock%2C+Amanda&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DUjRYKePKrB8C%26lpg%3DPR34%26pg%3DPR21%23v%3Donepage%26q%26f%3Dfalse&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAbolitionism" class="Z3988" about="#mwt83" id="mwAwc"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt83" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwAwg"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-28" id="cite_note-28"><a href="./Abolitionism#cite_ref-28" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-28" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation web" about="#mwt84" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite web","href":"./Template:Cite_web"},"params":{"title":{"wt":"The legal and diplomatic background to the seizure of foreign vessels by the Royal Navy"},"url":{"wt":"http://www.pdavis.nl/Background.htm#WAS"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAwk"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.pdavis.nl/Background.htm#WAS" id="mwAwo">"The legal and diplomatic background to the seizure of foreign vessels by the Royal Navy"</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=The+legal+and+diplomatic+background+to+the+seizure+of+foreign+vessels+by+the+Royal+Navy&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pdavis.nl%2FBackground.htm%23WAS&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAbolitionism" class="Z3988" about="#mwt84" id="mwAws"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt84" typeof="mw:Ex